{"tid":39284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚的一生","createTime":"2016-12-14T13:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:07:50.000Z","uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f90d8c9dd844118c6895fd2da1bc65d7d7a7c77f","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"升中四了，還未試過拍拖，但毒男說：「不緊要，依家努力讀書考好會考，第時有錢你荒（慌）無女？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，毒男克服了一個又一個的考試，升上大學；影畢業相時，發覺好多人都一雙一對，原來大學係撮合情侶既好地方。毒男依然一個，但他說：「不緊要，即將係我踏入社會大展拳腳既時候，亦係我幸福生活既開始！」<br />\n<br />\n毒男努力工作，三年，五年，七年過去了，依然單身。但他終於達成了心願，成為高收入人仕 － 月薪達二萬零五百蚊。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年過三十，開始疑惑：「點解我已經係成功人仕，但仲係無女？」更令他驚訝的是，公司不少女同事都同MK型男拍拖結婚，但那些男人可不是事業型喎，例如，Dorothy既男朋友只係中五畢業既Sales，月薪只有一萬八千蚊，比自己足足少了二千多元！點解？唔係努力讀書成為有錢人就有女既咩？<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺毒男到了中年，身邊已無什麼朋友，自己渡過一個又一個既聖誕節及情人節。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年老了，孤零零一個坐在公園，回想一生：「自己曾得過什麼？女人的身體是怎麼樣的？和女朋友係海邊共渡平安夜既滋味係點架？高登人不是經常留帖話：『後生時唔好浪費時間，第時有錢你荒無女咩！』我照做了，究竟什麼地方出錯？」"},{"pid":"5b8b82e9b2682f89ba94c2d10c8cc30cb3610914","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c243b9171eaaf3ae75185af59b58711f0a410f","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248657f4f1f0991667d5e79e59880666d6c88d8d","tid":39284,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6cc847bba4ac5d620dfb4f3c2cb419aadf2330","tid":39284,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b6746ec885c399487508fd4bef11fe693630a6","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf888ccee24b077c0345d1370f4c2fc68f0b0b4a","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"慘 毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbfd407a2d1a815d5be93fe8bc5fa1fe50a0b98","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4462f71a5b8cfc34eb19d9ad916a1e229068146d","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f0c57ddb9a707980dfcd20ba4521d61dd20953","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf5e859253ca31a205ba5037f6482dda4c39410","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6033873d03a1d8cf2d71a6a0a460b0aaee1e17f9","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be4e01932ad87f7fc0fabc8f355579a388175f3","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"十連冇難度？"},{"pid":"f07eefb625f583c150c4902561e9f000891486a1","tid":39284,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453fdc9d6a